# OSI model - 7 layers of networking

7. Application layer
  closest to the user, the actual application which user is using to interact with the network
  Firefox, Chrome, Outlook...
6. Presentation layer
  Operating System
  Device drivers
5. Session layer
  Communication between two computers
  session from user comp to webserver
  E.g. user can cat to the server but something in the backgourd stops working
4. Transport layer
  How much info should be sent
  transport of the data back and forth
3. Network layer
  Routers operate on this layer
  IP addresses
2. Data Link layer
  Switches operate on this layer
  MAC addresses
1. Physical layer
  Physical stuff that connects computers 
  pathes, cabling...
















